<dd class='comment-body' id='Blog1_cmt-2664849680246657472'>
<p>
Excellent post!  At first I was worried, but whew, I feel better now. We are a small publishing company.  We use CreateSpace for our POD services.  After the publishing process is complete we return the accounts (Amazon, dtp, Mobipocket) to the author.  We do not manage or take royalties.  Although, we will answer questions to help our customers with some marketing issues, that is not our expertise.  Our focus is publishing a quality product for a reasonable price and taking care of our customers.<br /><br />I&#39;m glad to have met you PublishingGuru.  Not only are you incredibly helpful, I may need to send some customers to you.
</p>
</dd>
