<p>
Lulu has no upfront costs and allows you to publish immediately.  Yes, books are too expensive, but they&#39;re a highly-useful service.  <br /><br />I published with Lulu for my first book, LSI for my second.  Obviously think LSI is superior, but you can&#39;t totally knock the convenience Lulu offers, and you pay for that convenience.
</p>
